'''The Crag''' was a jagged pinnacle of stone which overlooked the forests of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[H'ratth]]. [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Chamma]] often used its remote location for meditation with his apprentices.

